<td colspan=3 class=black><br><p><font class=b>How to play</font><br><font class=black>
Great in-game tutorial.  All pieces move like ordinary chess pieces.  To move drag your piece to a new square... or click on a piece and then the square you want to move to. In Kung Fu chess each move is timed.  You can move a piece, then need to wait for it to regenerate before moving it again. You can move more than one piece at a time.  Capture opponents King to win.<br><br>
<font class=b>Tips:</font><br>
 - Move fast, slow play will lose the game.<br>
 - If one piece is busy regenerating, use a different piece, don't wait around.<br><br>















